reviews.review_text:
Pitch is Waaay off at least a half-tone low (checked against a quartz-tuned strat w/freshly-set intonation.  The best source hands down for this source is:

http://www.archive.org/details/gd70-09-20.aud.remaster.sirmick.27583.sbeok.shnf

Truckin The Acoustic set was pretty tasty!

I especially enjoyed the acoustic Truckin.
Good to hear Bobby grind those lyrics!

Speedway offers some good advice
for the audiophile critics:
"Please don't dominate the rap Jack
if you got nothing new to say"

(dig the train whistle in intro  
  before Casey Jones...)
